#~ "All soldiers equipped with grenade launchers should carry at least one "
#~ "reload whenever they go out in the field. It is not advisable to send our "
#~ "troops into combat without spare grenades.\n"
#~ "\n"
#~ "\n"
#~ "Addenda\n"
#~ "\n"
#~ "None."
